import React,{ useState, useEffect } from 'react'; const MainPage = () => { const [bannerUrl, setBannerUrl] = useState("https://www.dunkindonuts.co.kr/menu/view?cat=1&sub=1&id=5587"); const [bannerImg, setBannerImg] = useState("/resources/img/2ICxlQlxjI6yOAPZFX3pGBpinqOUpCEAaO1cPqFm.png"); const [bannerBut, setBannerBut] = useState('bnBut1'); const [bannerIndex, setBannerIndex] = useState(1); const [bannerCount, setBannerCount] = useState(0); const [order,setOrder] = useState(1); useEffect(()=>{ time(); },[bannerIndex]) const time =()=>{ let num = order let bannerPlay = setInterval(() => { bannerButten(""+num); }, 5000); setTimeout(() => { clearInterval(bannerPlay); setOrder(num==3?1:num+1) }, 5000); } const bannerButten = (e) =>{ let pick = "" if(typeof e === 'string'){ pick = "bnBut"+e }else if (typeof e === 'event'){ pick = e.target.id } console.log(pick) if(pick === "bnBut1"){ document.getElementById('bnBut1').className = "bg-white rounded-full h-[7px] transition-all w-[7px] opacity-40 !opacity-100 !w-[20px]"; document.getElementById('bnBut2').className = "bg-white rounded-full h-[7px] transition-all w-[7px] opacity-40 "; document.getElementById('bnBut3').className = "bg-white rounded-full h-[7px] transition-all w-[7px] opacity-40 "; banner_img_href(1) setOrder(1) }else if(pick === "bnBut2"){ document.getElementById('bnBut1').className = "bg-white rounded-full h-[7px] transition-all w-[7px] opacity-40 "; document.getElementById('bnBut2').className = "bg-white rounded-full h-[7px] transition-all w-[7px] opacity-40 !opacity-100 !w-[20px] "; document.getElementById('bnBut3').className = "bg-white rounded-full h-[7px] transition-all w-[7px] opacity-40 "; banner_img_href(2) setOrder(2) }else if(pick === "bnBut3" ){ document.getElementById('bnBut1').className = "bg-white rounded-full h-[7px] transition-all w-[7px] opacity-40 "; document.getElementById('bnBut2').className = "bg-white rounded-full h-[7px] transition-all w-[7px] opacity-40 "; document.getElementById('bnBut3').className = "bg-white rounded-full h-[7px] transition-all w-[7px] opacity-40 !opacity-100 !w-[20px]"; banner_img_href(3) setOrder(3) } }; const banner_img_href = (num) =>{ console.log(num) switch(num){ case 1 : setBannerImg("/resources/img/2ICxlQlxjI6yOAPZFX3pGBpinqOUpCEAaO1cPqFm.png") setBannerUrl("https://www.dunkindonuts.co.kr/menu/view?cat=1&sub=1&id=5587") setBannerIndex(1) break; case 2 : setBannerImg("/resources/img/a7OUkDWNmrKd0i2DM7IefeE8lxOvUgIhCjtSX3Rd.png") setBannerUrl("https://www.dunkindonuts.co.kr/menu/viewProductCat?cat=3&sub=28&id=68") setBannerIndex(2) break; case 3 : setBannerImg("/resources/img/NhKu3wzNU0AOc48qysjJtksUVlbJS6bDLBjj7EEW.png") setBannerUrl("https://blog.naver.com/dunkin_kr/223580576950") setBannerIndex(3) break;
